Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then everything was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:35.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:47.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I should do anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Count to one hundred from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,One, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,four, five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:06.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Seventy-five, seventy-six, seventy-seven, seventy-eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Seventy-nine, eighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:13.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,eighty one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:20.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I was thinking I probably shouldn't interrupt, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:27.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:37.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:43.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After that, without having told me anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko and I parted at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning. {Good day doesn't sound right as a greeting.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:51.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko, are you participating in the treasure hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:10.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's not something you should be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:15.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At the beginning of the week, Touko returned back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:20.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:50.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's change location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi, you might not have noticed yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:06.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,my classmates were peeking at us with full interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:12.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But seeing us together shouldn't be that rare of a thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:16.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They knew that last year, I was excited when I received chocolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:20.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but I only accepted yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They were curious how I would look when-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:28.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to be the only one who knows how you look when you receive chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It feels like you're demanding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Surprising chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No. Level two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:50.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's so much love in them it'll surprise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,These are from me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Could these be chocolates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:06.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Last year, when you gave me chocolate, I was extremely happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:10.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So this year, I wanted to convey my feelings with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Am I the only one receiving these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're only for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For now, I want put a little distance between Touko-chan and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:32.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It seems like there was some kind of misunderstanding though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:40.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've decided to wait until Touko-chan decides to talk to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:50.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It really is a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,These are filled with so much love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's because, you were about to receive chocolate, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:19.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I was, but it's not something I wouldn't want others to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama's reaction just now was like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,a middle school boy who walked in when girls were changing, wasn't it?{loooooong}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:33.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, what I saw just now was worse than seeing girls change in a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The White Rose sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's like they're in their own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:45.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,From other people's view, the way Onee-sama and I looked just now was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Jeez! That's so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.03,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's really... {while}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,quite interesting watching Yumi-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, both the White Rose and the Red Rose families...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,enjoyed giving and receiving chocolate today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You guys must've been really busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:18.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, the head of the Yellow Rose family has exams so she's absent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-sama isn't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She said something along the lines of coming after her exam is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but I wonder if she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So, since everyone's gathered together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:31.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,let's start our final conference for the treasure hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:34.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Today's the day of the event, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about today's treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you going to show up or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even if I don't go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't believe there's any reason for it to be called "running away."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:13.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,From my eyes, it looks like you're running away from Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid of facing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're afraid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's because she's too honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:30.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She doesn't do this on purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But when she's with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,it feels like your weaknesses are being poked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:39.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's as if your self is being reflected back by an undistorted, unclouded mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't want to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even I've thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:48.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then why are you two still together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's because I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It certainly is difficult having your weaknesses prodded at,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:01.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but more importantly, it's more painful not being together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:06.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You know, I've started to think that if there are parts of me that I don't like,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,then it'll be good if I change those aspects
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:12.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,while I'm being reflected in the mirror that Yumi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:23.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've prepared myself for the one day that Yumi will find a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder, what kind of younger sister she'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's both fun and lonely thinking about what that girl will be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But Yumi can't be mistaken about who she chooses as her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:39.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's what I believed, and that's what I want to believe even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:42.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But you won't become my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:51.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I thought that the only person that would be able to be my rival at the treasure hunt would be you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:55.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing I can do if you aren't willing to stand at the start line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's quite a lot of people who have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sachiko-sama's there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, your fans are closing in around her little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That person! {In the background.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan came!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:43.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We will now begin the treasure hunt for the next Roses' treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Red, white, and yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:53.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,These cards are hidden separately within the area contained by the lines drawn on the maps provided. {long line is long}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The individuals who find a card
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,will receive the right to have a date for half a day with one of the next Roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If a card isn't found before the 4:40 time limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,we'll be giving a chance to the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:09.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,who couldn't make it, and thus placed a guess of the locations in the box beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For that reason, Nijo Noriko has declined to participate in the event itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and instead will be working as staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:23.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rosa Foetida, Hasekura Rei-sama, submitted her guess several days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rosa Chinensis, who will be participating,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,will be handicapped by waiting five minutes before starting her search.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This year, there are hints in different places as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so please do your best to find the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So then, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,None of you have to accompany me during my handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are we bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How about having tea together, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, isn't that a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,White roses...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What does "ku" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Apparently there's a total of nine characters for Shimako-sama's card hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There was a "ma" character stuck on the board of the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Where is it? {background}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:57.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did you find it? {Background}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They're at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:04.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The hint for the white card is "Ta-ku-ma-shi-no?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:08.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's not just in hiragana; there was a illustration of a bunny too, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I found another hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:17.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anyone's found Yoshino's card yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:19.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I pray that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,no one finds her card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and the right to have a date with her is given to me, who sent in a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino put that there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did you finish with your exam today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,May I have one more cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why has Sachiko-sama been drinking tea in this room this entire time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,instead of searching for your card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:11.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rosa Chinensis, do you already have an idea of where Yumi-sama's card is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:16.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean you've given up searching for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They're both wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:23.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I am participating in this event because I want to find Yumi's card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:27.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I can't find it if I just go around searching blindly, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here, waiting for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What're you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:38.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For Rosa Chinensis en bouton to let something slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:45.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but is it all right if I leave for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're concerned about her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. {Have a safe trip? Doesn't sound fitting.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:19.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When I was in primary school, they gave us new blank maps in social studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:24.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,At the time, I was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Apparently it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Blank maps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:46.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Was there an episode between you and Yumi-sama related to blank maps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:50.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did you think that Yumi-sama would want you to find the card,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:54.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so she would've put it in a place only the two of you would think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is that what you thought? {Sorry, a bit redundant here. But it's hard to divide the English the same way. Go ahead and try to divide the previous line before this one into 3 parts.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you going to laugh at my conceit? {Oh god, how do we make this shorter in English?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're treating Yumi-sama too lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama thinks of you preciously,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:13.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,but she's not someone that can only look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I knew that Touko now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,would be in this small room,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,searching for Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But no matter how much you search,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama isn't in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:33.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama has always been bigger than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So big that she can't enter this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's why you don't understand her, Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:49.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:56.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You were trying to break out of this narrow, suffocating situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought. Am I wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you're always smoldering on your own in a cramp place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to reach Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This way, you'll never be able to find Yumi-sama's card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Have you said whatever you wanted to say?{Haven't you just said whatever you wanted? Or "Have you said whatever you wanted to say?" but this meaning is a little less accurate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:32.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Since we're friends, I have to say things that need to be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Was it cold? Your nose is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:01.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What about the cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,None of them have been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sticking with just a second serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, do you think the red card will be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Has someone finally found a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I just brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:42.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You idiot! {Just keep this timed onscreen until the second to last one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:50.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino, you don't have to fire off so many "idiots"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with calling an idiot an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Show everyone what you've brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:02.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Valentine's Day Chocolate request order form?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I get into the college,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I figured the first thing I'd do is make Yoshino a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to make a cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:15.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I might as well take requests and make an amazing one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,An examinee like you shouldn't think about these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But bringing a yellow piece of paper like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,made us think that it was a card from the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, I found the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But it'd be bad if someone without the right to take it, took it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:32.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I pretended I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Chisato-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh? I can't be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have a good reason for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:44.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:49.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I have the yellow card here with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:59.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why did Sachiko-sama choose that person to be her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I hate the part of you that's so optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the Drama club right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're making such an unguarded expression again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Will you become my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If this is charity for this holy night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,please take it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's because she's too honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When she's with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,it feels like your weaknesses are being poked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then why are you two still together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's because I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:01.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Because... she loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Because she loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:35.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The yellow card was found by Chisato-san for the second year in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:39.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The white and red cards have yet to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Who will find my card, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:50.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:57.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,-ED-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:07.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,After the Valentine's Day plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:10.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I had a date with Tanuma Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.44,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It ended up being the same as the one she had with Rei-chan last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.44,0:24:18.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I ended up having a date with Iga Ami-san, who participated through the absentee guesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:22.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But that Ami-san wasn't the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:24.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And that's enough of that story!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.13,0:24:27.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What kind of date will Yumi-san and Touko-chan have?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.64,0:24:30.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next time: Searching for You.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.89,0:24:33.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Finally, I can reach Touko-chan.
